                "details": "<p>(trained) or <span data-pf2-check=\"perception\" data-pf2-traits=\"hazard,complex,fire,magical,trap\" data-pf2-label=\"Notice Control Panel DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"18\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Perception</span> check to notice the control panel</p>",
