        "details": {
            "description": "<p>A @Template[type:burst|distance:5] pillar of magical fire travels along a track throughout the room. The pillar emits bright light out to 20 feet.</p>",
            "disable": "<p><span data-pf2-check=\"arcana\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,fire,magical,trap,hazard\" data-pf2-label=\"Deactivate Control Panel DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"23\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Arcana</span> (trained) or <span data-pf2-check=\"thievery\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,fire,magical,trap,hazard\" data-pf2-label=\"Deactivate Control Panel DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"23\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Thievery</span> (trained) once on the control panel deactivates the whole trap, or <span data-pf2-check=\"thievery\" data-pf2-traits=\"complex,fire,magical,trap,hazard\" data-pf2-label=\"Deactivate Tracks DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"20\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Thievery</span> (trained) twice on the track prevents the pillar from moving. Each check requires two actions.</p>",
            "isComplex": true,
            "level": {
                "value": 3
            },
            "reset": "<p>The trap deactivates once it no longer detects the presence of creatures in the room.</p>",
            "routine": "<p>(2 actions) The pillar Strides, following the track in the room. If the trap&rsquo;s track is broken, the pillar can still Stride, but its Speed is only 15 feet. The pillar cannot move at all if the track is destroyed. When the pillar moves, it deals [[/r {1d10+6}[fire]]]{1d10+6 fire damage} to any creatures whose space it moves through.</p>"
        },
